  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3701820/" class="title-link">态度认真，可作一观</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3701820"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/4392009/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4392009-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4392009/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">斗草根</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-18"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-18 03:35:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3701820_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  中国大陆，谈犬儒的专著实在是凤毛麟角少得可怜，这本算是其中比较严肃的一种了。文字平实，无风无浪；结构分明，思路清晰。无甚奇绝之处，仅略占“严谨”二字。想对犬儒、犬儒现象、犬儒学派等有所了解的话，这本可作一观。

